Traverse each row, _m_, and subsequently each element, _a_.\
For each, traverse the remaining rows, _mn_, or _m + 1_.\
Compare each element, _b_ with _a_, implying _f_.\
Upon exiting the _mn_ traversal, assign the value where _f_ is _false_.

```java
